# --- Real welcome emails (Resend + `/api/subscribe`) ---
# The app POSTs to /api/subscribe by default (Vercel serverless + Vite dev middleware).
# Optional override: VITE_NEWSLETTER_API_URL=https://other-origin.com/api/subscribe
#
# Local dev: create .env.local (not committed) with:
#   RESEND_API_KEY=re_...
#   RESEND_FROM=Shoevera <onboarding@resend.dev>
#   (optional) RESEND_REPLY_TO, RESEND_SUBSCRIBE_BCC, WHATSAPP_NUMBER, WHATSAPP_MESSAGE
# Restart `npm run dev` after changing .env.local.
#
# Vercel production: set the same RESEND_* (and optional) vars in Project → Settings → Environment Variables.
#
# --- Optional: after a successful welcome send, also POST to your ESP list (Mailchimp, etc.) ---
# VITE_NEWSLETTER_FORM_ACTION=https://example.us21.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=...
#
# Resend test sender: with onboarding@resend.dev you can usually only send *to* your own account email until you verify a domain.
#
# Testing newsletter UI again: open /?reset_newsletter=1 (clears browser state and reloads).
